&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are Growers, We are Wholesalers, We are Producers, We Are Budtenders, We are Retailers, We are Partners, and We are Hiring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Holistic Industries is looking for an HR Generalist to join our team and support day-to-day people operations across multiple locations. This role is a key partner to leaders and team members, helping create a compliant, supportive, and engaging workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;You’ll play a hands-on role in employee relations, performance support, onboarding, and HR programs, serving as a trusted resource for both managers and team members while helping bring our culture to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted go-to for team members and managers, providing day-to-day HR guidance and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with leaders to navigate employee relations matters, including coaching, conflict resolution, and investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistent and compliant execution of performance management and corrective action processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain compliance across locations by supporting labor law adherence, policies, and HR best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver a smooth and welcoming onboarding experience, including new hire orientations and ongoing support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to a positive team member experience through engagement initiatives and clear communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support key HR programs and projects, helping improve processes and tools across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Strengths&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong foundation in employee relations with the ability to handle sensitive situations thoughtfully and fairly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to maintain confidentiality and demonstrate sound judgement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of HR policies, compliance requirements, and labor laws&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator who can translate HR guidance into practical, easy-to-understand direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized with strong attention to detail, especially with documentation and employee records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative partner who builds trust with leaders and team members at all levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable balancing multiple priorities in a fast-paced, multi-location environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
