&lt;li&gt;You have experience with operating a point-of-sale system, cash handling, and have meticulous attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are great at adapting and multi-tasking, showcasing your ability to handle multiple responsibilities efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capable of managing oneself and supervising others effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates strong ethical standards and sound judgment in decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
