&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Foster a warm and knowledgeable environment that encourages repeat visits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Share a comprehensive knowledge of cannabis-related topics, current trends, and provide valuable information to customers.&lt;/p&gt;
